  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package was signed at package-close and subsequently updated post-signing with a supplemental mesh-refinement validation result without re-signing; the supplemental evidence therefore carries a timestamp strictly after the package signature timestamp, triggering W-CON-03.",
